replies.body:
It actually isnt Riot's fault. If I recall, PAX explicitly said that Riot can not, and will not sell the PAX skins for any monetary value, at any time before or after the event, nor can they give away any of the skin codes before or after the event.

Thus, don't blame Riot, for I'm sure they would LOVE to make some money off of that AWESOME Pax Sivir skin. PAX Twisted Fate is actually regarded as the rarest skin in all of League of Legends. Do you know how much a code for that skin would go for?

And believe me, I know the pain. I SSSSSOOOOOO want that PAX Sivir skin. But, alas, I can't travel back in time. {{champion:32}}
